thread.title: lee ware
thread.title_full: Autoclick Rent a Car evaluado por lee ware

author: lee ware
title: lee ware
text: hired a car from autoclick for a week recently. this is a company that is off the airport. the pick up was on time with no waiting. getting the car was quicker than we have experienced with companies at the airport. the only reason I did not give 5 stars is that, as with all the car hire companies the extra insurance is way too high, and the thought of being charged for a small scratch is an unnecessary worry while relaxing on holiday.
